  p-范数双严格对角占优矩阵与新的矩阵特征值包含区域
  
  p-Norm DSDD Matrices and New Eigenvalue Localization Region
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>郑</surname><given-names>巧娟</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>李</surname><given-names>耀堂</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sup>1</sup></xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff2"><sup>2</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff1"><addr-line>云南大学数学与统计学院，云南 昆明</addr-line></aff><aff id="aff2"><addr-line>null</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>603795477@qq.com(郑巧)</email>;</corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>12</day><month>05</month><year>2017</year></pub-date><volume>06</volume><issue>03</issue><fpage>367</fpage><lpage>375</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
  给出一类新的非奇异矩阵——
  p-范数双严格对角占优矩阵(简记为p-范数DSDD矩阵)，并由其得到一个新的矩阵特征值包含区域。文中算例表明在某些情况下本文的矩阵特征值包含区域含于著名的Brauer- Cassini卵形区域之中。
   A new class of nonsingular matrices, 
  p-norm double strictly diagonally dominant matrices, (shorthand for p-norm DSDD matrices), is presented, and it is used to get a new eigenvalue inclusion region. A numerical example is given to show that the eigenvalue inclusion in this paper, in some cases, is in the famous Brauer-Cassini oval area.
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>p-范数DSDD矩阵，非奇异H-矩阵，特征值定位, p-Norm DSDD Matrix</kwd><kwd> Nonsingular H-Matrix</kwd><kwd> Eigenvalue Localization</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>p-范数双严格对角占优矩阵与新的矩阵特征值包含区域<sup> </sup></title><p>郑巧娟，李耀堂<sup>*</sup></p><p>云南大学数学与统计学院，云南 昆明</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20792-formula231"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x5_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2017年5月6日；录用日期：2017年5月24日；发布日期：2017年5月27日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20792-formula232"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x6_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>给出一类新的非奇异矩阵——p-范数双严格对角占优矩阵(简记为p-范数DSDD矩阵)，并由其得到一个新的矩阵特征值包含区域。文中算例表明在某些情况下本文的矩阵特征值包含区域含于著名的Brauer- Cassini卵形区域之中。</p><p>关键词 :p-范数DSDD矩阵，非奇异H-矩阵，特征值定位</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20792-formula233"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x7_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>Copyright &#169; 2017 by authors and Hans Publishers Inc.</p><p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY).</p><p>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</p><p><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html/htmlimages\1-2890033x\e70a10f1-7c93-45ea-9603-062237856e4b.png" /><img src="http://image.hanspub.org:8080\Html\htmlimages\1-2890033x\e898c85e-ffc4-45c9-b817-14224a4d6960.png" /></p></sec><sec id="s3"><title>1. 引言</title><p>矩阵特征值的包含区域在动力系统的稳定性分析，控制系统的可控制性研究，线性方程组的解法等问题的研究中有着重要的作用，是矩阵应用与分析中的一个重要课题。国内外许多学者都致力于这一问题的研究，无论是理论还是实用的需要，人们都希望用尽可能少的关于矩阵的信息与计算得到尽可能小的矩阵特征值包含区域以便更精确地定位矩阵特征值。本文继续矩阵特征值包含区域的研究，通过引进一类新的非奇异矩阵——p-范数DSDD矩阵，并由此给出一个新的矩阵特征值包含区域，在某些情况下改进了著名的矩阵特征值包含区域——Brauer-Cassini卵形区域。</p><p>首先给出文中所用的符号和术语。设n为自然数，记<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x10_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。q为正数或无穷大，记为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x11_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。设向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x12_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x13_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。记</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x15_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>特别地，(1) 当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x18_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x19_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；(2) 当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>下面我们回顾文 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref1">1</xref>] 中双严格对角占优(DSDD)矩阵的定义及其由此得到的矩阵特征值包含集。</p><p>定义1 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref1">1</xref>] 。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，如果对所有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x23_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x24_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，都有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>， (1.1)</p><p>则称<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为双严格对角占优矩阵，记为DSDD矩阵。</p><p>定理1 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref2">2</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref3">3</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref4">4</xref>] 。若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为双严格对角占优矩阵，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x28_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为非奇异的。</p><p>文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref5">5</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref6">6</xref>] 中给出了与双严格对角占优矩阵相对应的特征值包含区域：Brauer-Cassini卵形区域。</p><p>定理2 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref5">5</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref6">6</xref>] 。(Brauer定理)。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的所有特征值都包含在其<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x31_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>个Cassini卵形区域的并集之中，即</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.20792-formula234"><label>(1.2)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x32_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x33_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x34_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的谱(即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的所有特征值所成之集)，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>称为矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x37_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的Cassini卵形区域。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>2. p-范数DSDD矩阵</title><p>本节，我们引入一类新的非奇异矩阵：p-范数DSDD矩阵。为此先介绍p-范数SDD矩阵的定义 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref7">7</xref>] 。</p><p>定义2 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref7">7</xref>] 。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x38_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x39_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>. 若存在满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的正向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x42_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。 (2.1)</p><p>则称<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数SDD矩阵，其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的H&#246;lder补，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>定理3 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref7">7</xref>] 。若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数SDD矩阵，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为非奇异的。</p><p>下面定理给出p-范数SDD矩阵的一个充分必要条件。</p><p>定理4 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.20792-ref7">7</xref>] 。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x51_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数SDD矩阵当且仅当</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，(2.2)</p><p>其中，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x55_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x56_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x57_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的H&#246;lder补，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x58_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>受定义1、定义2及定理1和定理3的启发，我们提出如下问题。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x61_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。 (2.3)</p><p>那么<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是否为非奇异的呢？很显然，当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x65_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x66_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为双严格对角占优矩阵，则从定理1知，是非奇异的。那么，在一般情况下，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，条件(2.3)式能保证<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的非奇异性吗？我们先看如下例子。</p><p>例1。设</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x69_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x70_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，恒有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x72_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>但是，由于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x75_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，故<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为奇异的。</p><p>此例说明，一般来讲条件(2.3)式并不能保证矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的非奇异性。因此要保证<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的非奇异性，仍需要添加一些条件。</p><p>定理5。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。若存在满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的正向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="htt