nline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x126_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为非奇异的。</p><p>由定理5，我们可以给出p-范数DSDD矩阵的定义。</p><p>定义3。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x127_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x128_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。若存在满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x129_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的正向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x130_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>使得(2.4)式成立，即</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x131_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>则称<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x132_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵，其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x133_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x134_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的H&#246;lder补，因此<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x135_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>由定义3和定理5可直接得到如下定理。</p><p>定理6。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x136_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x137_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>非奇异。</p><p>下面我们给出p-范数DSDD矩阵的一个充分必要条件。</p><p>定理7。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x138_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x139_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x140_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵当且仅当</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x141_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。 (2.5)</p><p>证明：记<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x142_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x143_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为其的按行拉直向量，即</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x144_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x145_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x146_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x147_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x148_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的q-范数，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x149_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x150_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的H&#246;lder补，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x151_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>必要性，若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:hre