e"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>于是对任意的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x215_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x216_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>因为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x217_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则对任意的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x218_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x219_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x220_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>所以对任意的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x221_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x222_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>此式表明<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x223_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵。由定理6知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x224_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是非奇异的，因此<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x225_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这与(3.4)式矛盾。定理得证。</p></sec><sec id="s6"><title>4. 矩阵的特征值包含集</title><p>我们知道，每一类非奇异矩阵都对应一类矩阵的特征值包含集。由第2节的定理6知p-范数DSDD矩阵是非奇异的。本节就来讨论p-范数DSDD矩阵对应的矩阵特征值包含集。</p><p>定理9。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x226_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x227_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则对任意满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x228_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的正向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x229_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x230_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>， (4.1)</p><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x231_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x232_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x233_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的H&#246;lder补，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x234_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>证明：用反证法。假若有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x235_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，但<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x236_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则存在满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x237_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的正向量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x238_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得对任意<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x239_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x240_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>即矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x241_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵。由定理6知，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x242_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x243_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>矛盾。故对所有的<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x244_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，都有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x245_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，即<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x246_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>由定理7可以得到如下特征值包含区域。</p><p>定理10。设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x247_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x248_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x249_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>其中</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x250_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。 (4.3)</p><p>证明：设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x251_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x252_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.假若存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x253_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，使得<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x254_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x255_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。 (4.3)</p><p>设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x256_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x257_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>知，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x258_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，故<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x259_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为奇异矩阵。由<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x260_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>易得到</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x261_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x262_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x263_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x264_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>于是由(4.3)式可得</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x265_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>于是由定理7知矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x266_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为p-范数DSDD矩阵。再由定理8知矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x267_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为非奇异的，这与矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x268_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是奇异的相矛盾，故定理得证。</p><p>图1. 例2中矩阵A的特征值包含区域</p></sec><sec id="s7"><title>5. 数值例子</title><p>本节我们给出一个数值例子。该例表明在某些情况下定理10所给的矩阵特征值包含区域含于定理2给出的Brauer-Cassini卵形区域。</p><p>例2。设</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x270_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>由Matlab可计算出矩阵<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x271_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的全部特征值为−1.8444，4.5470，1.2974。图1中的绿色部分表示定理2中Brauer-Cassini卵形区域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x272_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，蓝色部分表示：当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x273_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，定理10中的矩阵特征包含区域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x274_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。由图1知，对此例而言定理10给出的特征值包含区域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x275_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>比定理2中的Brauer-Cassini卵形区域<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/17-2620413x276_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>要小。</p></sec><sec id="s8"><title>文章引用</title><p>郑巧娟,李耀堂. p-范数双严格对角占优矩阵与新的矩阵特征值包含区域p-Norm DSDD Matrices and New Eigenvalue Localization Region[J]. 应用数学进展, 2017, 06(03): 367-375. http://dx.doi.org/10.12677/AAM.2017.63042</p></sec><sec id="s9"><title>参考文献 (References)</title></sec></body><back><ref-list><title>References</title><ref id="hanspub.20792-ref1"><label>1</label><mixed-citation publication-type="other" xlink:type="simple">Li, B. (1997) Doubly Diagonally Dominant Matrices. Linear Algebra and Its Applications, 2